        </MudListItem>

        <MudListItem>
            <strong>Main Aim</strong>: Support staff members of GTA (Arma 3 Grand Theft ArmA) community a way to monitor and catch certain players
        </MudListItem>

        <MudListItem>
            <strong>Usage</strong>: The application is used by some of the staff members of GTA community
        </MudListItem>

        <MudListItem>
