    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" GutterBottom="true"> 
        <strong>Description</strong>:<br/>
        BattleMetrics Notifier is one of the oldest project in my portfolio which was written in .NET Framework 4.7.2. It has the following features:

        <MudList T="string">
            <MudListItem>
                <strong>Chat listening</strong>: The user can subscribe to certain messages in chat and get notified about it
            </MudListItem>

            <MudListItem>
                <strong>Players</strong>: Shows players who connected at specific time with e.g. less than 5 hours on the server
            </MudListItem>

            <MudListItem>
                <strong>Watchlist</strong>: The user can choose and watch certain players
            </MudListItem>

            <MudListItem>
                <strong>Discord List</strong>: Similar to Watchlist, the user can watch chosen Discord users
            </MudListItem>

            <MudListItem>
                <strong>BattlEye</strong>: The user can check BattlEye Global ban status of a player
            </MudListItem>
        </MudList>
    </MudText>
